name: Governor Mike Dunleavy
tweet: 4/4 This is not about exclusion. This is about protecting the gains women have made.

name: Governor Mike Dunleavy
tweet: 3/4 As a father of 3 women who participated in athletics and currently make a living in the resource extraction sector, which was not historically welcoming to women, I invite all Alaskans to understand the protection of these gains.

name: Governor Mike Dunleavy
tweet: 2/4 not just in competition in athletics, but in other endeavors that historically excluded women. I share his passion and I support those who wish to protect the gains made by women over the decades, including the protection of women’s athletics in Alaska.

name: Governor Mike Dunleavy
tweet: 1/4 As we celebrate the 50th anniversary of Title IX, we are reminded of how important competition is in the development of a human being. The late Sen. Ted Stevens was instrumental to the passage of Title IX and was a tireless advocate for women to have equal footing ...
